el\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 919}, {\"ngram\": \"three horses\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Horses have passports that include their travel and vaccine history.\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Horses\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"passports\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1019}, {\"ngram\": \"their travel and vaccine history\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Supplied: Chris Burke, IRT) To travel internationally humans must have a passport and horses are no different.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burke_(baseball)\", \"score\": 0.579208133955994, \"rank\": 0.6381387619445655, \"text\": \"Chris Burke\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burke_(baseball)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Burke_(baseball)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"IRT\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"humans\", \"from\": 1121, \"to\": 1127}, {\"ngram\": \"a passport\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the horses competing in the Olympics, their passport is issued by the International Federation for Equestrian Sports.\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1220}, {\"ngram\": \"their passport\", \"from\": 1222, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 1283, \"to\": 1300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This document includes what vaccinations the horses have received and their travel history.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This document\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Horses do not have photos in their passports.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1441, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Horses\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1402}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"their passports\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, there is a silhouette that has an outline and any unique markings or colours to help identify the horse, says Mr Burke.\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Burke\", \"score\": 0.960693682741348, \"rank\": 0.04091422179386806, \"text\": \"Burke\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Burke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Edmund_Burke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a silhouette\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"an outline\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"any unique markings\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"colours\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the main feature that identifies horses these days, like most animals is microchips,\\\" he says.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main feature\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1593}, {\"ngram\": \"horses\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1616}, {\"ngram\": \"most animals\", \"from\": 1634, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"microchips\", \"from\": 1650, \"to\": 1660}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is definitely in the passport.\\\"\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\":